<!doctype html>
<html lang=“en”>
{{> head }}
<body id="index">
  <div class="overflow-killer">
    {{> header }}
    <div class="content">

      <section id="headline">
        <img class="headline-gif gif" src="./img/header-flower.gif" alt="Animation of a flower growing.">
        <h1 class="headline druk">Locally sourced.</h1>
      </section>

      <section id="get-the-app">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="email-signup">
            <p><strong>A peer-to-peer stack for building software together. Sound fun?</strong></p>
            <form class="main-cta" action="https://formspree.io/xrgbwygl" method="POST" autocomplete="off">
              <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email here" required />
              <button type="submit">Sign me up</button>
              <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Subscription" />
              <input type="hidden" name="_format" value="plain" />
              <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="/subscribed.html" />
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="features">
        <img class="ui full-width float project-source" src="./img/ui/project-source.png" alt="Screenshot of a README file on the project page." />
        <img class="horizontal-scroll-gif gif" src="./img/extending-hands.gif" alt="Animation of a cartoon typing very fast. Each of his fingers split into 3 smaller cyborg fingers allowing him to type even faster.">

        <div class="container">
        
          <div class="attribute">
            <h4>For the collective</h4>
            <p>Support and be supported. Designed for sustainability.</p>
            <p>{{> svg-heart }} Fund projects and users</p>
            <p>{{> svg-currency }} Get paid for your work</p>
            <p>{{> svg-pen }} Form orgs independent of platforms</p>
            <p>{{> svg-network }} Create and redistribute wealth</p>
          </div>

          <div class="attribute">
            <h4>Local-first</h4>
            <p>All of your issues, revisions, and reviews exist on your computer. You own your data — nobody else.</p>
            <p>{{> svg-issues }} Manage issues locally</p>
            <p>{{> svg-loading }} No load times</p>
            <p>{{> svg-offline }} Work offline</p>
            <p>{{> svg-desktop }} Own your data</p>
          </div>

          <div class="attribute">
            <h4>Secure by design</h4>
            <p>No need to trust anyone to keep your work safe. Everything is backed by public key cryptography.</p>
            <p>{{> svg-user }} Cryptographic peer identities</p>
            <p>{{> svg-check }} Signed issues and code reviews</p>
            <p>{{> svg-multi-device }} Multi-device support</p>
            <p>{{> svg-key }} Verifable ownership proofs</p>
          </div>

          <div class="attribute">
            <h4>Peer-to-peer</h4>
            <p>No servers. No platforms. Share your code without relying on a third party.</p>
            <p>{{> svg-no-downtime }} No downtime</p>
            <p>{{> svg-everywhere }} Available everywhere</p>
            <p>{{> svg-eye }} Censorship-resistant</p>
            <p>{{> svg-free }} Free forever</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="protocols">
        <div class="container">
          <h1 class="druk">No more walled gardens.</h1>
          <div class="subtitle-container">
            <h2>Built on open protocols, not platforms.</h2>
          </div>
          <img class="protocol-gif gif" src="./img/garden.gif">
          <div class="protocols">
            <div class="protocol">
              <h3>Git</h3>
              <p>No need to change the way you work. Radicle extends Git with peer-to-peer networking, giving distributed version control a new superpower.
                <span class="links">
                  <a href="https://radicle.xyz/towards-decentralized-code-collaboration.html" target="_blank">More about our approach<span> ↗️</span></a>
                </span>
              </p>
              {{> svg-git }}
            </div>
            <div class="protocol">
              <h3>Radicle<br>Link</h3>
              <p>The new standard for code collaboration. Link is the peer-to-peer protocol that powers the Radicle Network. A network that everyone can use and no one can take down.
                <span class="links">
                  <a href="" target=>Documentation<span> ↗️</span></a>
                </span>
              </p>
              {{> svg-link }}
            </div>
            <div class="protocol">
              <div>
                <h3>Ethereum</h3>
                <span>(opt-in)</span>
              </div>
              <p>Harness the power of global identities and digital money. Fund and sustain your open source work without relying on intermediaries.
                <span class="links">
                  <a href="https://github.com/radicle-dev/radicle-contracts">Our contracts<span> ↗️</span></a>
                </span>
              </p>
              {{> svg-eth }}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="codelands">
        <div class="container">
          <h1 class="druk">Explore the codelands.</h1>
          <img class="codelands-gif gif" src="./img/blue-screen-of-death-walk.gif" alt="">
          <div class="two-column">
            <div class="two-column-item">
              <h3>Join the  Community</h3>
              <p>Everything is open-source and public by default.</p>
              <br>
              <p>Join our <a target="_blank" href="https://radicle.community/">radicle.community</a>.</p>
            </div>
            <div id="download" class="two-column-item">
              <h3>Try out the beta</h3>
              <p>Interested in integrating Radicle into your code collaboration experience?</p>
              <br>
              <a target="_blank" href="/">Download the beta<span> ↓</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="timeline">
        <div class="container">
          <h1 class="druk"><span class="italic">Where we’re headed </span>→</h1>
          <div class="subtitle-container">
            <h2>We see Radicle being the first open-source, community-led, self-sustaining network for software collaboration. <a href="/">Learn more about our plans</a>.</h2>
          </div>
          <img class="timeline-gif gif" src="./img/roadmap-flower.gif" alt="">
          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="line"></div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <p class="here">We're here</p>
              <div class="icon">
                {{> svg-here }}
              </div>
              <p class="date">Late 2020</p>
              <h3>β1 Release</h3>
              <p>The core feature-set on top of a peer-to-peer stack. This is when we'll start using it ourselves.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item not-active">
              <p class="not-here">not here</p>
              <div class="icon">
                {{> svg-date-square }}
              </div>
              <p class="date">Early 2021</p>
              <h3>β2 Release</h3>
              <p>The app will be hooked up with real money and the public registry and we’ll launch our native coin.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item not-active">
              <p class="not-here">not here</p>
              <div class="icon last">
                {{> svg-date-square }}
              </div>
              <p class="date">Late 2021</p>
              <h3>Version 1.0</h3>
              <p>Magic will happen. Everything will be solved and we’ll all be sillicon valley thousandaires.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
    </div>{{! closes content }}
    {{> footer }}
  </div>
</body>
</html>
